                        <h2><a href="http://www.baxi.co.uk/information-and-advice/how-to-videos.htm">How to videos&nbsp;&gt;</a></h2>
                        <p>From time to time, your Baxi boiler may need a
 bit of attention. It is quite normal for your boiler to need to be
reset or re-pressurised. These are small maintenance tasks that you may
be able to do easily without the need to call your installer.</p>
                        <p>To help you, we have created a number of video guides that will take you through the procedures very simply, step by step.</p>
